        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer745597186" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12139842968544647321">The simplicity of Moran’s writing style and storytelling grasps your attention. The story becomes addictive in small, measured steps and your imagination gets the better of you, that said, I found this to be a credible, fascinating look into this era of history. You can read full review on my blog: <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://poetryofreading.blogspot.com/2019/05/the-heretic-queen-by-michelle-moran.html'>https://poetryofreading.blogspot.com/...</a></span>
